<h1>The Realm of Capricorns</h1>
	<p><strong>Welcome to the realm of Capricorns! We are glad you are interested in our species, and this is the perfect place to learn more about us!</strong></p>
	<hr>
	<br>
	
<h3><em>What are Capricorns?</em></h3>
<ol>
  <li>Capricorns a unicorn-like species with a fascination for humans.</li>
  <li>They are usually male or female, with rare occasions of being born genderless.</li>
  <li>Capricorns often have a single human era of fashion that they love and create outfits themselves reflecting that era.</li>
  <li>They are a secluded and peaceful species living in communities around hidden areas of the universe.</li>
  <li>Each community has a different last name depending on where they live, making it easier to tell where another Capricorn is from.</li>
</ol>
	<br>
	
<h3><em>What do Capricorns look like?</em></h3>
<ul>
  <li>Around 4'4", with 3'5" min and 5'2" max.</li>
  <li>Adorned with a horn, ears, and a tail.</li>
  <li>Fashion matches that of favorite human era. </li>
  <li>Exact looks vary based on where they live. Examples below</li>
</ul>
	<br>
	<br>
	
